item.dc:creator: @oldskoolpk oldskoolpk
item.description:
@oldskoolpk wrote:

[center]What are you applying for?
Administrator or Webpage Developer
Why are you applying for this? Because I can enforce this server to become more friendly, and i want to help this team to be as successful since it’s got a lot of potential. I believe i have good leadership skills since i was capable of handling a 80+ server by myself, being the only coder/webpage developer. I have 3 years worth of experience with different roles such as: Moderators,Administrators, Co-Owner and I have ran a 317 private server with 350 members and a maximum of 80 players online.
www.projectosp.smffy.com
Why would you like to join the Miscellania team?
Because I feel that this team have a lot of potential and i would be an honour to join you guys whether as being an Administrator or a Moderator. And i would like to be more involved in more of these sort of events. I am capable:
Coding a 317 - I have been coding for currently a year now, and everyday I am being stronger and understanding the language.
developing a webpage - I can developt a very stable and working webpage.
Example:[color=blue] www.projectosp.smffy.com[/color]
Advertise - I have achieved 80 players to be logged in. and have 350 members on my older forums - www.oldskoolpk.tk
My server has gotten me a total of 160M in runescape money, which i sold for $3 each. and i recieved a total of $300 in 2 months. I want to move on to work with a proper team and learn from you guys.
What languages are you most confident/experienced in?

  • Spanish
  • English
  • Portuguese
  • Learning French.
    How old are you?
    16 - 26th of february 1995.
    Do you have; MSN, Skype, Ventrilo or any other sollution of the team contacting you?
    luisvictoria15_@hotmail.com

conclusion:
I have been very keen to work with a group like you guys, so i hope you guys accept me as a administrator. also, i do not mind developing a forums like mine. and I have connections to join the server. I have 350 members at the moment in this forums:

www.oldskoolpk.tk

I can also edit videos fairly well:

thank you for reading,
Luis[/center]

item.dc:creator: @Faze2 Faze ©
item.description:
@Faze2 wrote:

[center]
What are you applying for?
Global Moderator or Global Administrator.

Why are you applying for this?
I am applying as I would like to help you out. I want to be able to see that I have made an impact upon the community, allowing the members to have a more enjoyable time. I also want to make the job easier for yourself of any other developers, as you would have more time to focus on coding the server, and you wouldn’t have to concentrate as much on looking after what is going on inside the server.

Why would you like to join the Miscellania team?
Now, I’m going to say this. I don’t want to join the team if this project isn’t seen as serious. I’m not going to put my own time into making a server and forums as best as I possibly can, if you’re not going to try and keep it up for a long period of time. I have stated in the question before why I would like to join the team, I want to be able to help and see the community enjoy the server and forums.

What languages are you most confident/experienced in?
English? 0.o

How old are you?
13, and if you’re going to judge me because of my age, well then I’m not even going to bother talking to you. Age is but a number, and it is all down to a persons maturity. I don’t mean to sound rude by telling you that I won’t join if you judge me, but it’s true. I don’t want to be involved in a community which won’t give myself equal respect to that of an 18 year old etc…

Do you have; MSN, Skype, Ventrilo or any other sollution of the team contacting you?
Yes, I have all 3 of those things.
MSN - Faze_@live.co.uk
Skype - i_am_faze
I also have Ventrilo and I know how to use it etc…

Thanks for your time,
Faze.[/center]
